@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
title Component - Deploy webhook tự động

actor "GitHub" as GitHub
component "Nginx /webhook" as Nginx
component "itjob-webhook:9001" as Webhook
component "Git repository\n/var/www/EffortIT" as Repo
component "Build backend" as BackendBuild
component "Build frontend" as FrontendBuild
component "rsync dist" as Rsync
component "PM2 reload itjob-backend" as PM2
component "Nginx reload" as NginxReload

GitHub --> Nginx : POST webhook
Nginx --> Webhook : proxy request
Webhook --> Webhook : kiểm tra secret/branch
Webhook --> Repo : git fetch/reset
Webhook --> BackendBuild : npm install/build
Webhook --> FrontendBuild : npm install/build
FrontendBuild --> Rsync : copy dist
Webhook --> PM2 : reload backend
Webhook --> NginxReload : reload config nếu cần
@enduml

